  <title>Gio.Mount::remount_finish</title>
  <synopsis><code mime="text/x-gjs">
function vfunc_remount_finish(result: Gio.AsyncResult): Boolean {
}
  </code></synopsis>
  <p>Finishes remounting a mount. If any errors occurred during the operation,
@error will be set to contain the errors and <code>false</code> will be returned.</p>

<terms>
<item>
<title><code>result</code></title>
  <p>a <link xref="Gio.AsyncResult"/>.</p>
</item>
<item>
<title><code>Returns</code></title>
  <p><code>true</code> if the mount was successfully remounted. <code>false</code> otherwise.</p>
</item>
